FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our app for making foods.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What kind of foods can I make with this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app provides recipes and guidance for creating all types of dishes - appetizers, main courses, desserts, and more. Whether you want to cook up a quick snack or an elaborate meal, we've got you covered.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Do I need to be an experienced cook?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Not at all! Our app caters to both novice and experienced home cooks. We have simple recipes for beginners as well as more advanced options for skilled chefs.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I save my favorite recipes?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely. You can create an account and save recipes to your personal collection for easy access anytime.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, you can filter recipes based on various dietary needs and preferences such as vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, low-carb, and more.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Just download our app and start browsing recipes! You can search by ingredient, cuisine type, or dietary need. Tap on a recipe to view instructions and start cooking.

PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Cooking App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What types of recipes does the app offer?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app provides a vast collection of recipes spanning various cuisines, dietary preferences, and cooking styles. Whether you're looking for quick and easy meals, gourmet dishes, or something specific like vegan or gluten-free options, you'll find a wide range of recipes to explore.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I save my favorite recipes?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! Our app allows you to create a personalized recipe box where you can save your favorite recipes for easy access. You can also organize them into custom collections or categories for better organization.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Does the app provide nutritional information?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, we understand the importance of making informed dietary choices. Each recipe in our app includes detailed nutritional information, such as calories, macronutrients (proteins, carbs, and fats), and other relevant data like sodium and fiber content.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How can I share recipes with friends and family?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Our app makes it easy to share your favorite recipes with loved ones. You can simply copy the recipe link or use the built-in sharing options to send recipes via email, messaging apps, or social media platforms. Sharing delicious meals has never been easier!
PAGE_DETAIL_1_VALUE: Our app helps you plan, prep, and cook amazing homemade meals with ease. Access thousands of recipes, create custom meal plans, and get step-by-step guidance.
PAGE_DETAIL_2_VALUE: Automatically generate a grocery shopping list based on your meal plan. The list syncs across all your devices for convenient in-store access.
PAGE_DETAIL_3_VALUE: Easily filter recipes based on your dietary needs - vegan, gluten-free, keto, and more. We've got options to suit every lifestyle.
